    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow people to take a virtual driving test due to Covid",
        "additional_details": "Create a network in which invigilators can observe footage of learners driving to be able to make a decision on weather they pass or not.",
        "background": "Be able to take your driving test with your instructor and have it recorded or live streamed to an invigilator who can observe the driving and then decide whether they are a safe driver. This would reduce contact due to Covid and reduce waiting time to get a test.",
